ion',''),(894,2598,'location','[\"everywhere\"]'),(893,2598,'dismissable','1'),(319,2392,'mfn-page-items-seo','Heading\n\n<h4>ISLAND GIRL </h4>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n10px\n\nDesc\n\n<p>Hi there, \r\n<br><br>\r\nWhats up? \r\n<br><br>\r\nIm Shaira. My friends call me Sha. Thanks for dropping by! Since you are here, I am writing this letter to you to make sure we get to know each other a little better. \r\nMy goal is for you to get valuable insights from this site. In order for us to get to know  each other a little better and for me to gain your trust as well, let me share a few things about me. I\'d also love to hear about you so feel free to send me a message and say hi!</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nDesc\n\n<p><strong> </strong>\r\n<br><br>\r\n1. Like many Filipinos of my age, I am a registered nurse. I\'m a proud graduate of Cebu Doctors\' University. Like many others too, I decided to give up a career in Nursing. It was indeed a very difficult choice considering that I even took a specialization (Hemodialysis) and the fact that  it remains to be one of the most in demand professions abroad up to now. <br>\r\n\r\nYou can read about <a href=http://zerothreetwo.com/the-city/why-giving-up-my-white-uniform-was-the-best-decision-i-had-ever-made/\"#\">why giving up my white uniform was the best decision I have ever made HERE</a>.  This post unexpectedly became viral and every now and then, I still continue to receive messages about it. Still warms my heart every time! What\'s your nursing story? Let me know! \r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n2. I\'m a writer by passion. Ten years ago, I was already making extra bucks while studying by taking projects as a ghost writer. When blogging was not a big thing yet, I\'d keep handwritten notes and journals. When I say I\'m a writer by passion, I mean I love writing but that doesn\'t really mean I\'m good at it so if there\'s one person who reads what I put out there that would suffice for me. \r\n\r\n<br> \r\n\r\n3. What\'s really my job? A lot of people ask me this but most of the time, it\'s too complicated to explain to those who don\'t move around the Digital world. \r\nUntil now, I find it difficult to explain but let me just put it this way, whatever you see in the digital world, may it be a website, an app,etc., there are lot of people involved in coming up with that. What I do as an Operations Manager/Digital Marketing Manager is to ensure what you see works and doesn\'t suck! I\'ve worked \r\nwith virtual recruitment, web &app development and a whole lot of other stuff that\'s so far away from nursing! \r\n\r\n<br> \r\n\r\n4. So let\'s talk about travel! For the past year alone, I have been to  2 continents, 13 countries and 34 cities while working. \r\n\r\n</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nDesc\n\n<p><strong>Blogger by 21, Manager by 24 </strong>\r\n<br><br>\r\nAfter deciding to hang my white uniform, I have worked with different foreign companies and a lot of what I do revolves around digital marketing. I have been working as an Operations Manager for the past years. On the side, I have been contributing to different online publications such as Zerothreetwo and Two Monkeys Travel. Being with Zerothreetwo allowed me to further explore Cebu - from good food,  best resorts and everything else this beautiful island has to offer.  I come from  Mactan - the historic resort city! I grew up surrounded with water and up to this day, my office is by the water (although Im really not a good swimmer!) but this is where the Island Girl inspiration came from.\r\n</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n<img src=\"http://www.shairab.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Shaira-headshot-636x570.jpg\" alt=\"SHAIRA HEADSHOT\"/>\n\ncenter\n\nDesc\n\n<p><strong>Foodie, Coffee lover, Travel junkie</strong>\r\n<br><br>\r\nAside from food trips and undeniable love for coffee and fashion,I also like to travel. This past year alone, I have been to more than a dozen countries between Asia and Europe while working! This has been truly a fun learning experience for me. I am looking forward to share with you the travel tips and travel hacks I have discovered along the way as well as the various opportunities the digital world offers.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>Lets talk!</strong>\r\n<br><br>\r\nSo if you want to receive notifications and updates from the site, you can join my mailing list here.  I will also be hosting a number of giveaways, online sessions and actual brunch dates if we find ourselves in the same place!\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf you just want to say hi or ask me anything from nursing, digital marketing, restaurants, resorts, traveling or even life stuff, feel free to send me a message. Im always delighted to have a new friend who brings positivity and fresh ideas (Only negatrons are not welcome!) \r\n<br><br>\r\nPuss ochKram, \r\n<br><br>\r\nShaira B. \r\n </p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n30px 0 0 5%\n\n'),(799,2496,'mfn-page-items',''),(800,2496,'mfn-page-items-seo','<p>Like any lady, I love everything about fashion.</p><p>I confess to collecting many complicated swimsuits, shoes and boots.</p><p>After exploring many shop sites in the country, I realized that the fashion options are still quite limited. Therefore, I have put up a shop together to address this gap. =) </p>\n\n'),(801,2394,'_edit_lock','1514301475:1'),(804,2394,'_wpb_vc_js_status','false'),(802,2394,'_edit_last','1'),(803,2394,'slide_template','default'),(629,2500,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','2495'),(630,2500,'_menu_item_object_id','14'),(320,2394,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(321,2394,'_wp_page_template','default'),(322,2394,'mfn-post-hide-content','0'),(323,2394,'mfn-post-sidebar','0'),(324,2394,'mfn-post-sidebar2','0'),(325,2394,'mfn-post-slider','0'),(326,2394,'mfn-post-slider-layer','0'),(327,2394,'mfn-post-custom-layout','0'),(328,2394,'mfn-post-one-page','0'),(329,2394,'mfn-post-hide-title','0'),(330,2394,'mfn-post-remove-padding','1'),(331,2394,'mfn-post-menu','0'),(332,2394,'mfn-page-items',''),(333,2394,'mfn-page-items-seo','Heading\n\n<h4>I love to hear from anyone who visits this site. However, I also maintain a full-time job and still works on some digital ventures on the side while making sure I still have a social life so sometimes, messages in my inbox pile up. </h4>\r\n<div style=\"width: 110px; height: 4px; background: #db9d3a; display: inline-block;\"></div>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nDesc\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">BLOGGING, EVENTS, REVIEWS,ETC.</h4>\r\n<p>I have been attending events in Cebu for the past 5 years or so. I have done more than 50 reviews on restaurants, resorts,etc and all these can be found on Zerothreewo. Since I have been traveling and is temporarily based in Europe now, I can attend events here or anywhere around the continent. \r\n<br><br>\r\n*Please take note that I still do contribute for 032 but it will be my discretion if the article I write will be published here or on 032. \r\n</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n0 0 0 0\n\ndefault\n\nDesc\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center\";>WRITING PROJECTS & DIGITAL MARKETING NEEDS</h4>\r\n<p>I also personally take on writing projects. If you need someone to help you build your site, manage your social media accounts and help you with everything and anything you need to know about digital marketing, you can hit me up and I can show you a thing or two. \r\n<br><br>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center\";>TRAVEL TALK</h4>\r\n<p>After having enough travel experience, I have decided to help people with their travel plans. \r\nI have made many mistakes along the way and it could have saved me a lot of money, time,etc. if I knew better earlier or if someone who had given me a clear recommendations. Based on my experience, stuff on the internet is too mixed up while agencies give very limited information. Connect with me and lets talk about making sure your visa gets approved and all other important things get taken cared of to ensure that your dream Eurotrip can come true! \r\n</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n0 0 0 0\n\n<h4>To get in touch with me, please consider the following:</h4>\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf the other options dont work for you, fill out the message box below. \r\n<br><br>\r\nIll do my best to respond to you within 24 hours and I look forward to work<br>or even just have a good chat with you!\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n[cn-social-icon]\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nContact form\n\n[wpforms id=\"2549\" title=\"false\" description=\"false\"]\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n'),(808,2548,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(809,2549,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(334,2459,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(335,2459,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(336,2459,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(337,2459,'_menu_item_object_id','2394'),(338,2459,'_menu_item_object','page'),(339,2459,'_menu_item_target',''),(340,2459,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(341,2459,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(342,2459,'_menu_item_url',''),(343,2459,'menu-item-mfn-megamenu',''),(344,2459,'menu-item-mfn-bg',''),(345,2460,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(346,2460,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(347,2460,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(348,2460,'_menu_item_object_id','2392'),(349,2460,'_menu_item_object','page'),(350,2460,'_menu_item_target',''),(351,2460,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(352,2460,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(353,2460,'_menu_item_url',''),(354,2460,'menu-item-mfn-megamenu',''),(355,2460,'menu-item-mfn-bg',''),(356,2399,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(357,2399,'_wp_page_template','default'),(358,2399,'mfn-post-hide-content','0'),(359,2399,'mfn-post-sidebar','0'),(360,2399,'mfn-post-sidebar2','0'),(361,2399,'mfn-post-slider','0'),(362,2399,'mfn-post-slider-layer','0'),(363,2399,'mfn-post-custom-layout','0'),(364,2399